At first sight, POOCHYENA takes a bite
at anything that moves.
This POKMON chases after prey until the victim becomes exhausted.
However, it may turn tail if the prey
strikes back.

POOCHYENA is an omnivore - it will eat
anything. A distinguishing feature is
how large its fangs are compared to its body. This POKMON tries to
intimidate its foes by making the hair
on its tail bristle out.

It savagely threatens foes with bared
fangs. It chases after fleeing targets
tenaciously. It turns tail and runs,
however, if the foe strikes back.

It has a very tenacious nature. Its acute
sense of smell lets it chase a chosen
prey without ever losing track.

Medhyna est dun temprament tenace.
Son odorat trs dvelopp lui permet de ne jamais
perdre la trace de sa proie.

Es hat ein hartnckiges Wesen. Sein prziser

nachzujagen, ohne die Fhrte zu verlieren.

Es tenaz por naturaleza. Tiene un sentido del olfato

It has a very tenacious nature. Its acute sense of
smell lets it chase a chosen prey without ever

Sans se poser de questions, Medhyna essaie de mordre
tout ce qui bouge. Ce Pokmon pourchasse sa proie jusqu
ce quelle spuise. Cependant, il se peut quil prenne peur
et senfuie si la proie riposte.

Sobald Fiffyen eine Bewegung wahrnimmt, schnappt es zu.
Es jagt seine Beute so lange, bis sie vollkommen erschpft ist.
Wenn sich die Beute allerdings wehrt, kann es passieren,
dass Fiffyen klein beigibt und flieht.

La primera reaccin que Poochyena tiene al ver algo moverse
es darle un mordisco. Este Pokmon persigue a su presa hasta
que cae agotada. Aunque, a veces, sale huyendo si su presa
le responde con un ataque.

Poochyena azzanna al minimo movimento senza riflettere.
Caccia la sua preda finch questa non  tanto stanca
da cedere. Tuttavia, se il nemico contrattacca, Poochyena
talvolta scappa.

Poochyena es un Pokmon omnvoro. Se come lo que sea.
Le caracteriza el gran tamao de sus colmillos respecto al
resto del cuerpo. Este Pokmon hace que se le erice la cola
para intentar intimidar a su rival.

Poochyena  onnivoro: mangia di tutto. Una caratteristica
distintiva  la dimensione delle zanne rispetto al corpo.
Cerca di intimidire i nemici rizzando il pelo della coda.
